Class Logarithm

java.lang.Object
org.tweetyproject.math.term.Term
org.tweetyproject.math.term.FunctionalTerm
org.tweetyproject.math.term.Logarithm
public class Logarithm extends FunctionalTerm
Instances of this class represent application of the logarithm function on some term.

Matthias Thimm
